Checks: >
  -*,
  cert-*,
  clang-analyzer-*,
  clang-diagnostic-*,
  concurrency-*,
  cppcoreguidelines-*,
  hicpp-*,
  misc-*,
  modernize-,
  performance-*,
  portability-*,
  readability-*,
